## Note on tool names

Tool names referenced anywhere in this wiki are *proposed* — derived
from frontend call sites. The actual MCP server does not exist yet. See
[`tools-proposed.json`](tools-proposed.json) for the full machine-readable
list intended for whoever wires up the MCP server.

Flow files do not name proposed tools at all; they reference intents
defined in [`glossary.md`](glossary.md), which is the single indirection
layer that maps intents to currently-proposed tool names. When tools are
renamed, only the glossary updates.

